data.description: GRACIOUS LIVING.  This outstanding three bedroom two bath home was built in 2022 and is absolutely gorgeous.  Thoughtfully designed for relaxed living and entertaining, it offers 9’ ceilings, granite countertops, plush bathrooms, spacious living room, informal dining bar, large U shaped kitchen configuration, double sink vanity in primary bedroom, and front and back covered porches.  This home shows the pride of ownership, is in impeccable condition, and ready for your enjoyment.  The home is situated in Del Mar subdivision, just minutes from Gun Barrel City. Homeowners have access to nearby boat launch, dock, pavilion, and park with basketball court.
